column5: Any ideas heading into May of being out by the opener?
Should be no problem, it appears it is going to be a normal ice out in this part of the world.

Main lake still mostly covered. North end, Canoe, Steam Boat channels are open. Look for Trappers Point Camp on face book. He is putting out update every couple days. Will be on the lake May 18th. Ice out should be perfect for the opener this year.
